==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Revolting
<hw>Re*volt"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Causing abhorrence mixed with
disgust; exciting extreme repugnance; loathsome; <as>as,
<ex>revolting</ex> cruelty</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Re*volt"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Revoluble</ent>⟦br⟧
